{
  "stem": "22910.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you know, here again in retrospect, why on earth was it so important for those Germans to give up railroad space, cars, manpower to schlep us from place to place when all they have to do is abandon us?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by that time it was the-- the-- the British who would have freed us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just schlepped us from place to place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and really that they-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] it was to the disadvantage of their war effort.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Oh, boy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a terrible thing-- they must have forgotten to disconnect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they gave up all this time and space and equipment and manpower just to schlep us from place to place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And finally, we came to Porta Westfalica.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was going to be spring already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were able to find some-- some gray and try and cook it, because there's very little food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the way, during all this time, there was no organized feeding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There just was no such thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you heard a rumor that over there somewhere, they're handing-- passing out soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By time you got there, there wasn't any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or sometimes you did make it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And once, I-- I made it, and I got some soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by that time, we had a transport of-- of gypsies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the gypsies got hold of me and took my soup away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Towards the end, I-- I met some gypsies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the way, I still can't understand this business of the gypsies having been killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure that there were many killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the town I come from, there were three kinds of gypsies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One kind became just wondering gypsies.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
